yproduct, we clarify which renormalization scheme must be\nused for squark masses in loop corrections to low-energy quantities such as the\nB-B-bar mixing amplitude.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 3 Aug 2019 19:31:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-06"}
