e Trie are almost\nsimilar but both perform many times better than Hash Tree in the distributed\ncomputing environment of Spark.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 4 Aug 2019 13:13:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-06"}
