len equivalence. Lastly,\nworking with the notion of Quillen bifibration, we show that there are model\ncategories of stratified spaces and of stratified simplicial sets. We show that\nthe two are related by an adjunction that preserve weak equivalences.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 4 Aug 2019 15:47:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-06"}
